author: hughesj
msg: Previously:
downloads directory: prerequisite downloads such as xmlschema and xerces
classes directory: woden classes
classesapi directory: API classes when buildAPI target run
classestest directory: test classes when buildTests target run
All these dirs were peers with the 'java' directory.
If running inside eclipse:
a) project had to be called 'java'
b) the above directories were created as children of the workspace directory, so not visible from the woden project in eclipse once ant had finished.
Therefore:
1) downloads directory now a child of java
2) classes, classesapi and classestest children of java/build
also:
3) added showProperties target to show all the properties used. init now depends on showProperties
